----------------------------------------------------------------------------

AAARGH!

    At the start of each screen you'll find various buildings.
Blow fire over them, and then hit them. This will make them fall down
a lot faster. When you burn or knock down a house you get an egg.
    To beat the other monsters in a fight for an egg, don't jump around and 
breath fire, just hold your ground and punch forward.  After three or four 
falls, your foe will stay down.  
    Keep eating, even if it dosen't show any increase on screen, your health
will skyrocket.
___________________________________________________________________________

ACTION FIGHTER

Get on the hi-score table and enter ZBACKDOOR for infinite lives.
____________________________________________________________________________

ADDAM'S FAMILY

In case you don't already know....to get 4 free lives each time your
game has ended, walk past the CONTINUE DOOR to the left and there is a
room where you can collect them!

Go up immediately into the hall of rooms, walk left until you are under
the door above you...push up. You are now in a secret room.  Collect the
stuff in that room, THEN walk up directly up that door and push up--there
you will find a MASS amount of treasures, 1 UPS, and other goodies!
----------

Useful codes in the game (not sure where you use them)

  First power-up    &1#1#             L1191 - extra energy
  Second power-up   ?1S1M             61H1C - rescue Pugsley
  Third power-up    BLSRS             B&198 - rescue Granny
  Pugsley           V121B             B?KKV - rescue Fenster
  Wednesday         VD2RL             BLS1T - rescue Wednesday
  Granny            V&YKW
  Fester            VL#R4             (Second column from Amiga Power)

