AFTERBURNER

Pause the game , then type THUNDERBLADE. Then try the following keys:

  < - Go down a level
  > - Go up a level
  G - More Missiles
  T - Less Missiles
  N - Extra Lives

Fly to the top of the screeen to avoid missiles.  Slow down on levels
8 and 17 to avoid rocks.  Go full speed to dodge infra-red missiles.

Note: Other sources say type TOGETHER IN ELECTRIC DREAMS
__________________________________________________________________________

AFTER THE WAR

To give yourself infinite energy & time, press the following three keys 
simultaneously on level 1;

  Hold down the  ALT, 1, B  keys.

  Holding down the  ALT, 1, M  keys advances you to the second level.

  The password for Level 2 is 101069.
____________________________________________________________________________

AGONY

Hit any one of the following keys during play to activate these cheats.

  F1  Puts a sword underneath your owl.
  F2  Puts a sword above your owl.
  F3  Increases the size of your bullets.

Press F3 three times to gain an extra live. This cheat can be repeated
often so watch out you don't run out of lives.

Note: Another sourse says you need to type FANTASY first then type F1-F5
      for various cheats. Pressing the Return key then skips levels.
____________________________________________________________________________

AIRBALL

The spellbook is in the room with the candle. You have to pick up and 
remove the blocks to get it. Take the spellbook back to the start screen, 
drop it in the top left corner and follow the instructions to get the 
ingredients to complete the game. 
___________________________________________________________________________

ALIEN BREED

To activate the following cheats, log onto the terminal on deck two (one
screen south of where you start) and simply type in (including spaces) one
of the following:

I CANT BE ARSED TO PLAY THE FIRST LEVELS - sends you directly to deck 3
ALIENS ARE FAGGOTS - makes the aliens quite weak
PUFFNUTS MODE - makes the aliens quite slow
IS IT TRUE THAT THE ALIENS SUPPORT MAN UTD - , makes the aliens very weak
PISSED AS A FART - to paaly the game in drunken mode
PITBULLS ON THE LOOSE - makes the aliens as dangerous as pitbull terriers
BEN JOHNSON TRAINED THESE ALIENS - makes the aliens a bit faster
THE IRAQIS MADE THE WEAPONS - gives you absolutely abysmal weapons
SALMAN RUSHIE PLAYS ALIEN BREED - all the aliens flee in terror
BEWARE ALIENS SPADGE HAS DROPPED ONE
________________

The best method of disposing of the end of level guardians is to stay at the
very bottom of the screen and continously shoot at the nasties. The guardians
will almost touch you at times, but if you stay firmly at the bottom, they
won't harm you.
