DARK CASTLE

The first thing you do is to go to the shield room.
Once there press (W) up and (S) down.
Keep them both pressed.
This will cause your hero to go up and down between the two screens.
After half an hour or so you will have about 25 lives, this is the only
screen you can do it on.
