DAYS OF THUNDER

Type in COME FLY WITH ME (on title screen?)
---------------
Enter the qualifying race as normal and pause the game (P).  Now type
COMEFLYWITHME.  The screen should flash to confirm the code, and when you
un-pause the game you can pull back on the joystick and soar into the air.
Use the fire-button to move forward and the function keys to get a view of
yourself flying through the sky.
