GOLDRUNNER

Type 'EASYMODE' on the high-score table.  From now on, F9 skips levels
and makes you invulnerable.  F8 turns off the cheat mode.

Start a one player game and crash into the first building. Now hold down the
'F5' key until the status screen appears. You should now be able to fly
unscathed through everything.

Press 'F2', 'F5', 'F4', 'F3' one at a time in that order. You then have
infinite speed, lives, and energy.

Hold down F5 for a few seconds for an indestructable ship, press I to move
onto the bonus screen and press U to leave it again.  By continually 
pressing I and U it is possible to skip all the levels.
