KEEF THE THIEF

For something interesting in this game go up into the tree houses near
the left side of the map. When you see a commercial like screen with a
woman in it make this spell: Rhino Horn, Black Pearl, Narcicus Root.
___________________________________________________________________________

KICK OFF:

As the computer or a friend is getting ready to take a shot, just hold
down the fire button and the result will either be your keeper saving
the ball or knocking it over the net.
__________________________________________________________________________

KICK OFF 2

Keep pressing 'R' when you take a penalty.  This will show you where the
player's going to kick the ball.
