In is hard to believe, but Amiga Action magazine says the cheat for this
game is the same as for the first Nebulus. Type HELLOIAMJMP (no spaces)
on the title screen to gain infinite lives. Access to any unfinished
tower is activated by the function keys F1 to F8.
