PINBALL FANTASIES

After you loaded a pinball table and it scrolls up and down
you can enter these codes (WITH spaces, no Return required):

       FAIR PLAY           -  Disables all previously entered cheats
       EARTHQUAKE          -  You may 'tilt' the table as you like
       EXTRA BALLS         -  Gives you 5 balls instead of 3
       DIGITAL ILLUSIONS   -  The ball cannot leave the table
                              (You can only leave the game by pressing
                               'P' for pause and ESC to quit the table)
       VACUUM CLEANER      -  Clears the highscore list
