___________________________________________________________________________

ROBOCOD

Type in the password is LITTLE M to bring up the level selection screen.
Then you type in 1-50 for desired levels. - Amiga Power cheat.

Type in THE LITTLE MERMAID complete with spaces at any time during the game,
including the title sequence.Press the following keys to activate the cheats.

     F    Gives James wings
     X    Takes you straight to the exit
     P    Gives you the airplane, but only on some levels
     B    Gives you the bathtub, but again, only on certain levels
     M    Warps you to any place in the game
     F9   Strange screen effects (useless but worth a view)
     F10  More useless screen effects

To become invulnerable, hit the CTRL key to make the border flash, then
press Return. To deactivate the cheat, press Return a second time.

To activate the everlasting shield, collect the following objects:
cake, hammer, earth, apple, tap. The first letter of each object name
spells a word; i.e. cheat.
Make your way through the first door, go right and look for another five
objects. To obtain full power with each new life pick up the next five
objects thus; penguin, oil can, wine glass, earth, racket (spells power).
Finally to gain infinite lives move to the right until you find yet another
five objects close together and collect these as follows; lips, ice cream,
viola, earth, snowman (spells lives).

There is a secret room. Walk along until you get to the first ramp (jumping
over the doors as you go) and jump up to the roof on your right. Walk left
and you should go into the side of the building, leading you to the secret
room.

Complete a level which doesn't feature a Guardian and you will always find
something new when you return to the castle `selection' screen.

Finish the bath levels and as soon as you come out of the door run straight
to the golden snowmen in the bottom far left outside the castle. Jump into
these snowmen and you'll float upwards to the top of the screen where you'll
be met by a door. Getting through this door is tricky but worth it. Inside
are loads of extra lives and energy stars.
Go to the same place after finishing the circus room (the last room before
the end of game baddy) and stand on the golden snowmen again. A platform
made of two bonus blocks ahould float upwards revealing a secret tunnel. At
the end of this are even more extra lives and stars.
