RODLAND

Begin play and pause the action. Press the Help key exactly five times
(no more, no less). Unpause to resume play and the cheat mode will be
active. You will have INFINITE lives and you can advance to the next
scene when you press the Space Bar. Hopefully you should see a tiny love
heart at the top of the score and status panel that will show that the
cheat is active.
