SHADOW WARRIORS

During intro screen press CTRL, ESC, F2, 5, V, J, Right Alt, Help, Left 
bracket  & Enter on numeric pad. (May require a friend to help press all
the keys together.) Now when the title screen plays the bottom of the screen
will flash to indicate that the cheat is activated. 
During play the Help keys skips levels.
Q key turns off the collision detection

Another cheat:

When you reach the continue option screen and, if after the word credit, it
says 1, start tapping the 1 and 2 keys alternately, all the way through
the change disk prompt until both men fall from the sky. This gives you
infinite lives.
