STORMLORD:

First cheat:

On the credits screen type 'DRAGONBRIDGE' (no spaces) a scrolly
message should come across saying "You cheating swine", in-game press
the 'SPACE BAR' to pause and then press 'L' to skip the level.
Also another cheat is: when the game starts to load hold down the mouse
button and the joystick fire button and keep them held down until the 
game loads. Then when the game starts pause it straight away and type
'MNBVC'. This will give you infinite time and lives, and if you pause
the game and press 'L' you will advance a level.

Another cheat: Could be for Atari ST?

   As the game starts to load hold down left mouse button and firebutton,
   and keep them down until game loads. Then when the game starts pause it
   and type MNBVC for infinite time and lives. Pause game and press L to
   skip to the next level.

Another cheat:

Enter 'JAMES CAMERON' on the high score table.  Now, whenever you need more
lives, hit F9.
