STRIDER II

Press following keys together - HELP, left Amiga and 1 key. 
Pressing 1-5 will skip through the levels and F1-F4 will teleport Strider
to the corresponding level.
NOTE: One source says its the left Shift key not left Amiga key.

Start the game and type `SWIFT'. A cheat icon should appear and now pressing
`E' will replenish Strider's energy, while `D' will replenish the Strider
robot's energy. 
