table and enter your name. Now start the game again, press fire so you can move
about.
Stand still (preferably no where near the guards !!) and type
'DISCOVERYSOFTWARE' and press RETURN (you should see a message on screen) You
will now have infinite lives & go onto the next level. Now when you press
RETURN at any time during play you will automatically go to the next level.
